{"tid":2094821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】刑滿出獄獲百人迎接 勇武派無悔抗爭：原來大家冇忘記我","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T04:04:56.000Z","uid":54517,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"884b33e1df9441799afd19fbb59760c9ed502614","tid":2094821,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/P3PEST67SMSF4MVB4TSTN6JNRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FP3PEST67SMSF4MVB4TSTN6JNRQ%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=db7910a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FP3PEST67SMSF4MVB4TSTN6JNRQ%2F&h=394b6dfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/P3PEST67SMSF4MVB4TSTN6JNRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n「撐手足、撐到底！」6.12一周年早上，近百人於攝氏30多度烈日高溫下在監獄外靜候同路人。有人捧着鮮花，有人揮動「光復香港、時代革命」旗幟，1B手足（化名）就是當日出獄的抗爭者。經歷逾半年的囚禁，人生因此改寫，但他指從不後悔，僅因不能與其他前線抗爭者齊上齊落感遺憾。面對未來不安，他寄語同路人要堅持，更想與獄中抗爭者說：「好多人都冇忘記身在監獄嘅佢哋。」<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得當日見到義士行出黎,大家個種開心同安心呀??我想話大家唔好放棄呀,團結係我地最大武器,唔好比恐懼打倒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當日個POST</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2058999/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2058999/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2e3c17877261d93c97709e4211987d067fd5a244","tid":2094821,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgm